claim.claim-text:
1. A disc case comprising: 
a container member; 
a cover extended from one side of said container member; 
a pair of opposite latches in said container member each comprising a base in one end coupled to a bottom of said container member, and a latched piece coupled to the other upward free end of said latch being extended outwardly; and 
a flexible bridge interconnected the free ends of said latches for forming a first integral member.
